body: Still encountered a similar issue on 1.4 while using [import_pb_to_tensorboard.py](https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/master/tensorflow/python/tools/import_pb_to_tensorboard.py) to analyse a graph. Was able to use it by replacing the graph load from file with a [saved_model load](https://www.tensorflow.org/programmers_guide/saved_model#loading_a_savedmodel_in_python).
